rockchip-vaapi (1.0.4-1) noble; urgency=low

  * Add MOZ_ENABLE_WAYLAND=1 to environment: Firefox uses Wayland natively
    when WAYLAND_DISPLAY is set (e.g. sway), enabling full DMABUF zero-copy.
  * Add MOZ_X11_EGL=1 to environment: Firefox uses EGL on X11 sessions,
    enabling hardware WebRender via Mali-G610 (panthor/panfrost, GLES 3.1).

 -- Eduardo García-Mádico Portabella <woodyst@gmail.com>  Fri, 25 Apr 2026 14:30:00 +0000

rockchip-vaapi (1.0.3-1) noble; urgency=low

  * Add debconf question to configure system-wide VA-API environment variables.
  * Install /etc/profile.d/rockchip-vaapi.sh (terminal sessions).
  * Install /etc/environment.d/60-rockchip-vaapi.conf (systemd desktop sessions).
  * Supports dpkg-reconfigure to change the choice after installation.

 -- Eduardo García-Mádico Portabella <woodyst@gmail.com>  Thu, 24 Apr 2026 15:00:00 +0000

