rockchip-vaapi (1.0.0-1) noble; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * VA-API 1.20 vtable implementation bridging libva to librockchip-mpp1.
  * H.264 hardware decode with DRM PRIME 2 zero-copy surface export.
  * H.264 Annex B SPS/PPS reconstruction via Exp-Golomb encoding.

 -- Eduardo García-Mádico Portabella <woodyst@gmail.com>  Thu, 24 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0000
